# Aipify Enterprise Polish

Build production software — no placeholders, dead ends, or unfinished pages.

## Loading states

Use centered `AipifyLoader` (symbol + animation). Do **not** show visible text like Loading…, Initializing…, Rendering…, or Preparing…

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD — animation only; sr-only for accessibility
<AipifyLoader centered fullPage />

// ❌ BAD
<AipifyLoader label="Preparing dashboard…" />
<p>Loading...</p>
```

## Empty states

Never show empty white pages. Every empty state needs:

- Title
- Explanation
- Recommended action
- Primary CTA

Prefer `PlatformEmptyState` over plain text.

## Module cards

Each card: module name · one-line description · clear CTA. Never expose translation keys, raw IDs, or internal labels.

## Error states

Never expose stack traces, type errors, or raw API responses.

Use calm enterprise copy + Retry action:

> Something unexpected happened. Our team has been notified. Please try again.

## Internal strings

Forbidden in UI: `superAdmin.*`, `aiAssistant.*`, `translation.*`, raw `modules.*` keys. Use human-readable enterprise copy via i18n.

## Design principle

A user should never wonder "Is this finished?" Every screen must communicate confidence.
